A cyberpunk aerial view of two vast cityscapes connected by streams of glowing fiber optic cables stretching across a dark ocean at night, one city ultra-modern with towering holographic displays and neon-lit skyscrapers, the other emerging with scattered lights growing brighter where the cables touch down, digital data particles flowing like rivers of light between both shores, dramatic perspective from above showing the contrast between connected and connecting worlds, deep purples and electric blues dominating the color palette with warm orange accents where technology blooms.
